<main>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" id="active-favors">
            <div class="col s5">
                <img src="assets/images/goodvibes.jpg" width="90%">
            </div>
            <div class="col s6">
                <h3>Active Favors</h3>
                <div class="row" id="search"></div>
                <form>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="material-icons prefix">search</i>
                        <input id="search" required placeholder="Search for an Active Favor">
                        <label for="icon_prefix">Search</label>
                    </div>
                </form>
                <ul>
                    <lh id="favor">{{#each activeFavor}}
                        <li class="activeFavors">
                            <p class="label"> {{this.favor_name}} </p>
                            <p class="label"> {{this.favor_price}} </p>
                        </li>
                    </lh>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s1"></div>
        <div class="row" id="ask-favors">
            <div class="col s1"></div>
            <div class="col s10">
                <h3 style="color:#42A5F5">Ask a Favor!</h3>
                <hr>
            </div>
            <div class="col s1"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" id="favors-form-row">
            <div class="col s1"></div>
            <div class="col s5">
                <p>Suppose you needed a hand with something.
                    <br>Maybe you have a closet that needs to be sorted through and you can't get motivated to do it. Perhaps
                    you need a friend to watch your kid for an hour so you can run some errands.
                    <br>Going away on vacation?...Who is going to feed your cat? </br>
                    <strong>Karma to the rescue!</strong> Karma is an app where a group of friends can ask for and give help. Each
                    group member will be assigned Karma Koins when they join. They will have the option to ask for assistance
                    by entering the task they need help with, the date, and how many Karma Koins it "pays". They can also
                    see the list of tasks that others need done and can select which ones they will help with. You can only
                    ask for help if you have Karma Koins to offer so no one gets to always ask for help and never help others.
                    <br> Examples of information that can be accessed...history of tasks completed, history of help requested,
                    Karma Koins remaining, members of your group.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="col s1"></div>
            <div class="col s4">
                <div class="newFavors">
                    <form class="create-form">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="newFavorName" name="newFavorName" class="textarea_msg" placeholder="Enter Favor Name here">
                            <input type="text" id="newFavorDesc" name="newFavorDesc" class="textarea_msg" placeholder="Enter Favor Description here">
                            <input type="text" id="newFavorPrice" name="newFavorPrice" class="textarea_msg" placeholder="Enter Number of Karma Koins offered">
                        </div>
                        <button id="submitBtn" class="submitBtn" type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col s1"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

